हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: When love is worshipped as sacred, betrayal cuts deeper than a wound. A heart that once trusted unconditionally now drowns in deception and despair. This is a haunting tale of emotional ruin, lost innocence, and the fight to survive the unthinkable.
